  "description": "The tape is physically disintegrating. Delay feedback near self-oscillation — the echo becomes its own instrument. Spring reverb at 0.95 means the room is now louder than the source. Wow/flutter at 0.7 makes pitch a suggestion. Drive colors everything with amber distortion. The original note is a rumor.",
